This package was debianized by Yann Dirson <dirson@debian.org> in May 2002.
It maintained since late 2007 by Daniel Leidert <daniel.leidert@wgdd.de>.

It was downloaded from the docbook SVN repository at

  http://docbook.svn.sourceforge.net

  To prepare the source tarball, the get-orig-source target in debian/rules
  should be used.

